{"Name":"Lorong Puntong GLS","ShortName":"Lorong Puntong GLS","Description":"Lorong Puntong GLS is approximately 46,284 sqft and is expected to yield around 140 units. Located within the Bishan planning area, the site sits at the fringe of established private residential enclaves in Sin Ming and Upper Thomson, and its proximity to Bright Hill MRT and Ai Tong School makes it a highly desirable location for families. ","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/3ff997df-8264-4777-9cfd-9efa03b5608c","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/3ff997df-8264-4777-9cfd-9efa03b5608c","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}